<i>Welcome to Ridge Valley High..</i>

00:07.529 --> 00:10.765
'...conference
today in the auditorium.'

00:10.767 --> 00:12.967
<i>...tech billionaire
Tobias Bloom's</i>

00:12.969 --> 00:16.471
<i>innovative center for learning</i>

00:16.473 --> 00:18.872
<i>where the youth of today</i>

00:18.874 --> 00:22.242
<i>become the leaders of tomorrow.</i>

00:22.244 --> 00:24.945
<i>Tobias Bloom invested
in Ridge Valley High</i>

